Plot: The Baltimore-set movie of interconnecting story arcs deals with the challenges of reading or misreading human behavior.
Title: He's Just Not That Into You
Writer: Abby Kohn, Marc Silverstein, Greg Behrendt (book), Liz Tuccillo (book)
Actors: Morgan Lily, Trenton Rogers, Michelle Carmichael, Jasmine Woods
tomatoConsensus: Despite the best efforts of a talented cast, He's Just Not That Into You devotes too little time to each of its protagonists, thus reducing them to stereotypes.
